        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: RAB11A was detected in SV biochemical fractions, and enriched as compared to the P2 fraction.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Brain Synaptosomes and SV Purifications. Synaptosomes (P2') and SVs were purified from whole brain of 4- to 6-wk-old Sprague-Dawley rats following the same protocols used in ref. 2 and previously described in ref. 34 for SV, and in ref. 4 for P2'.\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0098993 replaced by GO:0030672" ;
